2010-06-17  Stefan Haller  <haliner@googlemail.com>

  Version 0.5:
  * dvr-recover.py: Minor Bugfixes.
  * dvr-recover.py: Direct access to Windows device files forbidden.
  * dvr-recover.py: Use Sqlite3 database instead of chunk list file.
  * dvr-recover.py: All settings are stored in database now. Use the parameter
    "setup" to manipulate the preferences.


